  "description": "Annual herb from Malvaceae, native to tropical Africa and cultivated across Middle East, Mediterranean, and Asia since ancient times. Heat-loving; produces mucilaginous leaves used in traditional Palestinian, Egyptian, Lebanese, and Indian cuisines. Seeds carry cultural lineage through generations and diaspora communities.",
